Package hoonigan

Hoonigan This is a simple package, which contains all relevant classes for the Hoonigan Library Program.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    Book class A simple Book class--extended from Abstract Library_Items class
    CD
    CD class A simple CD class--extended from Abstract Library_Items class
    DVD
    DVD class A simple DVD class--extended from Abstract Library_Items class
    FileInfo
    FileInfo class This class takes an array found in a JSON file, and parses the elements into an ArrayList, based on the parsing rules found in the HowToParseLibraryItems class.
    HowToParseLibraryItems
    HowToParseLibraryItems class This class defines the Parsing Rules, which will determine how the GSON Parser parses the JSON file
    InitializeProgram
    InitializeProgram class This class instantiates a Parser object, which reads a JSON file, Parses the JSON file, and stores the Elements within the JSON file into a HashMap.
    Library_Items
    Library_Items abstract class An abstract class, which extends into four Subclasses: Magazine, Book, CD, DVD
    LibraryUI
    LibraryUI class This class is the starting point for our software.
    Magazine
    Magazine class A simple Magazine class--extended from Abstract Library_Items class
    Parser
    Parser class This class instantiates the Gson parser, and reads a JSON file that is passed in through Parser().
